@node "Disclaimer" "Disclaimer"

 - Disclaimer - 

The  authors of  AmyBW can not be held responsible for any damage that this
program  or  the  manual  that  came with it might cause.  If you are using
AmyBW,  you  will  do  so  at YOUR OWN RISK.  Note however that it has been
